3. The diuers meanes are discouered,
whereby Satan foretells things to come;
as, by true Creatures.

div.p:
This is done,Of enchātment, and it vnlawfulnesse, I proued by the effects. first, by Enchantment;
namely, when by some Charme
wonderous workes are wrought.

4 As detaining them thereby in
Atheisme and contempt of Gods Ordinances
for saluation,
